extendedInfo.description: Application to Go Contacts with nice clouds on a blue background. A friendly application with the motif of clouds. Clouds are in cartoon style. The background main manu of contacts is blue.Name of contact is in dark blue color, date and time are white. The keyboard keys are little white clouds, numbers and letters are in blue. Button for calling has a white background, black caption and little claus motif with rainbow. On the bottom you can see piece of blue cloud, the rest of the elements are blue.  If you like nice and cute motifs and if you like cartoons and tale, this theme may be the best for you. Clouds and blue background enliven your phone and make the contact list will not be so boring and gray. If you really like our theme of clouds in cartoon style, also check out our other designs with cute animals in cartoon style. The application of the clouds to Go Contacts is free.Requirements:This theme requires GO Contacts EX application installed on your phone.
